comment: LATR and LHH show that Anderson (NOP) maintains legal guarding position as he contests Cousins' (SAC) driving dunk attempt.
Cunningham (NOP) cleanly strips the ball from Rondo (SAC).
Acy (SAC) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Davis (NOP) away from the ball. As he stays with Davis, he makes incidental contact with Cole (NOP) who attempts to set a screen.
Rondo (SAC) makes contact with Holiday (NOP) that affects his RSBQ and causes him to lose control of the ball.
Cole (NOP) makes contact with Cousins (SAC) that causes him to lose control of the ball.
Perkins (NOP) makes contact with Cousins' (SAC) body that affects his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Holiday (NOP) makes incidental contact with Belinelli (SAC) that does not affect his FOM away from the ball.
Rondo (SAC) commits a take foul on Cole (NOP).
Holiday (NOP) cleanly strips the ball from Collison (SAC).
